{"tid":1046256,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸客佔領出入口　港男拍片大罵　再出絕招","createTime":"2019-03-04T06:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T10:38:34.000Z","uid":225464,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4cfd4a90e63f05313b14a5c0f935157274097280","tid":1046256,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T06:02:15.000Z","msg":"<strong>大陸客佔領出入口 港男拍片大罵 再出絕招</strong><br />\n<br />\n片LINK：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2EJ3BOG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2EJ3BOG&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4BkIbV9%2FoY%2BmeTBoP0X2IjM%3D&h=f2d2aae5\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2EJ3BOG</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190304/photo/bkn-20190304132654166-0304_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190304135154\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190304%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190304132654166-0304_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190304135154&h=e36def5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁叫人點出入呀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上水一向是水貨客活躍的地方，不少人會在地上開篋整理「戰利品」，嚴重阻塞街道。近日有街坊為抵抗內地客，竟然採用水攻之法？<br />\n<br />\n有網民星期六（2日）上傳片段至Facebook群組「North District 北區」，只見有近10個內地客攜同行李篋坐在新康街的商店及大廈門前，地上放滿大包小包的商品。<br />\n<br />\n有人更將行李篋攤放在大廈樓梯口整理，阻塞他人進出。拍片者大感困擾，上前直斥︰「有冇搞錯呀，擺晒啲嘢喺門口」，又指若他們不移開物品，「我叫上面倒水落嚟」。<br />\n<br />\n從他上傳的另一張相片可見，大廈對開的街道濕透，亦不見有遊客堵塞在門前。<br />\n<br />\n網民紛紛笑言︰「夠鐘洗地」、「支持十五分鐘洗一次」、「地方清潔人人愛」、「水攻最佳辦法」。"},{"pid":"bf2a37031a356e6fb4a015c6197deff5b2a77efb","tid":1046256,"uid":136760,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T06:04:00.000Z","msg":"津路水炮大戰蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf6396eeb6672dcb1491d476dca97cae2dec1b4","tid":1046256,"uid":16676,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T07:05:00.000Z","msg":"條友係樓上網吧老闆<br />\nd 水貨欄住個門口, 封住個入口<br />\n阻住佢d 客仔上去幫襯<br />\n緊係嬲嬲豬啦<br />\n(條金鏈粗過口)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57abcbba9a6db43d74b9db6857c409bfb0bfc4b","tid":1046256,"uid":28397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T07:25:54.000Z","msg":"好橋 駁條冷氣機喉 慢慢滴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa28d65c2e7e76d685a8d08ba9a7e42b40a4a8b","tid":1046256,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T10:15:32.000Z","msg":"拍片有鬼用咩直接撞埋去"},{"pid":"69a4d0da195d13490a16087235cf24fb217c5e93","tid":1046256,"uid":180576,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T10:38:34.000Z","msg":"要鬥賤先對付到"}]}